cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper deals with trust evaluation models in e-commerce environments, which involves the computation of trust values based on transaction data. This falls under the domain of database systems (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also addresses the problem of malicious sellers deceiving buyers, which is a security issue (cs.CR). The proposed approaches involve indexing and data structures, which are topics in information systems (cs.SI) and cryptography and security (cs.CY).
